pathway.author: [Mikikot, Afukushima, Khanspers]

comments.content:
This pathway describes the glucosinolate derived from aromatic amino acid (Phe, Tyr, Trp) in Arabidopsis thaliana. This is based on the KEGG pathway and PlantCyc.

Some pathway entities are unknown and being investigated, these are denoted as "Catalyst" and "Metabolite" for now.
